body_html:
This solved it for me:

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/50609845/tensorflow-1-8-0-with-python-3-6-4-in-anaconda-show-error-dataset-ops-so-not-fo/50942347

"follow this path and locate _dataset_ops.so

D:\programfiles\Anaconda3\envs\tensorflow\Lib\site-packages\tensorflow\contrib\data

then move _dataset_ops.so file out of that folder to another location."
